Yetunde Odunuga (amuru na ọnwa 19 Nọvemba  nke afọ 1997) bu onye amateur onye Naijiria nke meriri ihe nrite ọla n’egwuregwu Commonwealth 2018
Ọ meriri nrite ọla n'ime mmemme etiti arọ megide Caroline Veyre
N'afọ 2017, Yetunde Odunuga, onye ọrụ ndị agha Naijiria nwetara ọla edo n'ụdị dị fechaa nke ụmụnwaanyị n'asọmpi ịkụ ọkpọ Amateur Africa, Brazzaville, Congo
Ịgba ọkpọ | Usoro ihe omume kwa ụbọchị - Gold Coast 2018 Commonwealth Games
